OL,3,CTravel disruption over Easter Weekend
OL,4,Cwith station and line closures
OL,6,FLondoners are being advised to check
OL,7,Fbefore travelling with disruption
OL,8,Facross the capital.
OL,10,FThere will be work happening at major
OL,11,Fstations, as well as the closure of
OL,12,Fsome tube lines across the whole of
OL,13,FEaster weekend.
OL,15,FPeople will be travelling home to
OL,16,Ffriends and family with motoring
OL,17,Fservices company the RAC predicting it
OL,18,Fwill be the busiest Easter on the
OL,19,Froads since 2022.
OL,21,FBut, what's happening in the capital?
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
