OL,3,CTravel disruption over Easter Weekend
OL,4,Cwith station and line closures
OL,6,FEuston Station
OL,8,FThere will be no trains between Euston
OL,9,Fand Milton Keynes from Friday 3 April
OL,10,Funtil Wednesday 8 April as "major
OL,11,Fimprovement works" take place.
OL,13,FThis means that services between
OL,14,FScotland, the north-west of England,
OL,15,Fthe west Midlands and London will
OL,16,Fterminate at Milton Keynes Central.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
