PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1775574665
OL,3,CTravel disruption over Easter Weekend
OL,4,Cwith station and line closures
OL,6,FBuses will run between Milton Keynes
OL,7,FCentral and Bedford / Potters Bar
OL,8,Fwhere you can catch a train to and
OL,9,Ffrom an alternative central London
OL,10,Fstation.
OL,12,FWaterloo Station
OL,14,FThere will be a reduced service
OL,15,Fbetween Waterloo and Clapham Junction
OL,16,Ffrom Friday 3 April to Monday 6 April
OL,17,Fas part of vital upgrades.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
