OL,3,CTravel disruption over Easter Weekend
OL,4,Cwith station and line closures
OL,6,FNational rail say passengers may need
OL,7,Fto change trains at Clapham Junction
OL,8,Ffor services to and from London
OL,9,FWaterloo. Queenstown Road Battersea
OL,10,Fstation will be closed throughout.
OL,12,FTransport for London also have
OL,13,Fclosures in place across the tube
OL,14,Fnetwork between Good Friday and Easter
OL,15,FMonday.
OL,17,FThe A40 closures are also in place as
OL,18,Fof Friday 20 March until late April.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
