OL,3,CTravel disruption over Easter Weekend
OL,4,Cwith station and line closures
OL,6,FIt is closed in both directions
OL,7,Fbetween the Westway roundabout and
OL,8,FMarylebone Flyover and will be in
OL,9,Fplace across Easter Weekend.
OL,11,FTransport For London warns that
OL,12,Fdrivers can expect "severe delays"
OL,13,Fduring peak times and diversion routes
OL,14,Fand local roads will be extremely
OL,15,Fbusy,.
